{"lastModified":1771255842261,"uri":"c::8346777690::vessel::5a094e00-4125-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nWelcome to the world of “Dream,” a captivating Oceanis 46.1 sailing yacht that beckons you to explore the open waters. Crafted in 2023, this vessel encapsulates modern luxury and timeless elegance, offering an experience that goes beyond the ordinary.\n\nA Glimpse into “Dream”:\n\n• Modern Aesthetics: “Dream” stands as a testament to the art of yacht design, with sleek lines and a spacious deck layout that seamlessly blends style and function.\n• 2023 Creation: Immerse yourself in the latest yacht construction advancements, sailing confidently in both comfort and safety.\n• Ultimate Comfort: Experience luxury in motion with onboard air conditioning for a pleasant climate and a generator ensuring consistent power supply.\n• Seafaring Independence: “Dream” features a state-of-the-art watermaker system, providing you with fresh, desalinated water for the entirety of your voyage.\n• Grand Entrance: A stunning gangway featuring stainless steel and teak accents welcomes you and your guests aboard in style.\n\nYour Voyage of Discovery:\n\n“Dream” opens the doors to limitless exploration. Whether you’re a seasoned sailor or new to yachting, our vessel promises an unparalleled journey. Feel the rush of wind, the gentle roll of waves, and the serenity of boundless ocean views. “Dream” isn’t just a yacht; it’s your gateway to discovering the world’s oceans in a whole new light.\n\nReserve Your Passage:\n\nReady to set sail on “Dream”? Contact us now to secure your spot onboard. Whether you’re seeking solace, romance, or family bonding, “Dream” ensures an unforgettable maritime escapade in 2023 and beyond.","blueprint":{"name":"DREAM","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::5a094e00-4125-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219::assets::e74e8c60-4127-11f0-afa5-35fb39f516b8/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5a094e00-41